Class PrivateBoardSpace<T extends Title>

java.lang.Object
org.douggschwind.games.boardgames.monopoly.space.BoardSpace
org.douggschwind.games.boardgames.monopoly.space.PrivateBoardSpace<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
PropertyBoardSpace, RailroadBoardSpace, UtilityBoardSpace
public abstract class PrivateBoardSpace<T extends Title> extends BoardSpace
Instances of this class represent board spaces that can be privately held and thus purchased or sold by a player. One of the properties, railroads, or utilities.
